data.title: S E P O R A // WestSydCreative
data.content:
•• #NewSelfWales •• Firstly, you should use that hashtag if you want your portrait to be featured in a new immersive exhibition at the State Library of NSW... and if you’re as narcissistic as me 💁🏾
••••
Lastly, if you want to see this face in the flesh, I’m playing Hot Gin Punch at @GiantDwarfHQ this Saturday 11/08, a new variety night brought to you by @MothersRuinCab queens @MaeveGoBash & @Liabzann! In partnership with @fourpillarsgin, all audience members will get a FREE G&T on arrival. Tickets available in my bio, come along and say hi-yo 👋
